739a7104-3161-4cdb-824e-4c8e2f336bd7.title: Master Chef
739a7104-3161-4cdb-824e-4c8e2f336bd7.text:
Ah! Welcome, newcomer. I am the Master Chef, Lev. It
is here I will teach you how to cook food truly fit for a
king.

8e9f9333-5dbf-475b-8028-fc4d5cc0ec01.title: <player>
8e9f9333-5dbf-475b-8028-fc4d5cc0ec01.text:
I already know how to cook. Brynna taught me just
now.

26bf796a-6566-47ce-8966-1b0e55793dbf.title: Master Chef
26bf796a-6566-47ce-8966-1b0e55793dbf.text:
Hahahahahaha! You call THAT cooking? Some shrimp
on an open log fire? Oh, no, no, no. I am going to
teach you the fine art of cooking bread.

args: Combine the ingredients to make dough.

78172ef6-8f76-4bdb-8be6-2168f0852d7f.title: What would you like to hear more about?

94a47939-c6bd-41f0-87ab-9359e1cbefb9.title: <player>
94a47939-c6bd-41f0-87ab-9359e1cbefb9.text: Tell me about range cooking again.

2f04c0db-c675-41b7-b4d1-b43b6f9cc886.title: Master Chef
2f04c0db-c675-41b7-b4d1-b43b6f9cc886.text:
The range is the only place you can cook a lot of the
more complex foods in MineScape. To cook on a
range, hold the item you would like to cook,
then left click the range.

83058092-5c5d-4b67-8394-438b0cea945f.title: Master Chef
83058092-5c5d-4b67-8394-438b0cea945f.text:
To listen to music whilst roaming the world click on
the music icon in your inventory, then click the link.
in chat.

e2b29bdb-1df2-41d2-99e4-f15bd485ae7c.title: <player>
e2b29bdb-1df2-41d2-99e4-f15bd485ae7c.text: Tell me about making dough again.

b6578178-966f-4361-8a84-04e7324d6ff7.title: Master Chef
b6578178-966f-4361-8a84-04e7324d6ff7.text:
It's quite simple: just use a pot of flour on a bucket of
water, or vice versa, and you'll make dough. You can
also refill your bucket at the sink.
